data.description: Introducing a stunning custom-built 3 bedroom home nestled on a spacious 2.5-acre lot in the beautiful New Smyrna Beach. This exceptional property offers a rare opportunity for horse enthusiasts, as horses are permitted on the premises. Situated on a high and dry lot, the land has been meticulously cleared, providing a blank canvas for your outdoor aspirations. Whether you envision creating a tranquil oasis, designing a lush garden, or constructing additional structures, the possibilities are endless. Step inside the home, and you'll immediately appreciate the craftsmanship and attention to detail that went into its construction. Built in 2021, this residence boasts modern features and contemporary finishes that cater to a comfortable and luxurious lifestyle. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the spacious living areas, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The kitchen, equipped with top-of-the-line appliances and ample counter space, is a chef's dream come true. It's the perfect place to prepare delicious meals while entertaining family and friends. The three bedrooms offer ample space for relaxation and privacy. The master suite is a true retreat, complete with a well-appointed ensuite bathroom and a walk-in closet. Wake up to breathtaking views of the surrounding natural beauty and start each day feeling rejuvenated. Outside, the expansive yard provides ample room for outdoor activities and entertainment. Whether you want to host gatherings, set up a playground, or simply enjoy the tranquility of nature, this property offers endless possibilities. Located in New Smyrna Beach, you'll have easy access to the area's pristine beaches, vibrant downtown scene, and excellent dining options. Enjoy the best of both worlds with the privacy and serenity of the countryside while still being close to all the amenities and attractions the city has to offer. Don't miss out on this extraordinary opportunity to own a custom-built home on 2.5 acres of land in New Smyrna Beach. Embrace a lifestyle of luxury, nature, and endless possibilities. Contact us today to schedule a private tour and experience the beauty of this property firsthand.
